      "type": "concept_card",
      "cpa_phase": "abstract",
      "title": "Roll Over the Hour",
      "content": "When adding minutes pushes past 60, roll over: 4:50 + 30 min. 50+30=80. 80=60+20. So 4:50+30=5:20. Always check if you crossed the hour.",
